{"id":250,"ayahs":[{"number":6,"arabic":"وَيَسْتَعْجِلُونَكَ بِٱلسَّيِّئَةِ قَبْلَ ٱلْحَسَنَةِ وَقَدْ خَلَتْ مِن قَبْلِهِمُ ٱلْمَثُلَٰتُ ۗ وَإِنَّ رَبَّكَ لَذُو مَغْفِرَةٍۢ لِّلنَّاسِ عَلَىٰ ظُلْمِهِمْ ۖ وَإِنَّ رَبَّكَ لَشَدِيدُ ٱلْعِقَابِ","translation":"And [since, O Prophet, they are bent on denying the truth,] they challenge thee to hasten the coming upon them of evil instead of [hoping for] good although [they ought to know that] the exemplary punishments [which they now deride] have indeed come to pass before their time. Now, behold, thy Sustainer is full of forgiveness unto men despite all their evildoing: but, behold, thy Sustainer is [also] truly severe in retribution!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1713.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":6946,"position":1,"arabic":"وَيَسْتَعْجِلُونَكَ","translation":"এবং তোমার কাছে তারা তাড়াহুড়ো করছে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6947,"position":2,"arabic":"بِٱلسَّيِّئَةِ","translation":"ব্যাপারে মন্দের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6948,"position":3,"arabic":"قَبْلَ","translation":"পূর্বে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6949,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْحَسَنَةِ","translation":"ভালোর","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6950,"position":5,"arabic":"وَقَدْ","translation":"অথচ নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6951,"position":6,"arabic":"خَلَتْ","translation":"গত হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6952,"position":7,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকেই","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6953,"position":8,"arabic":"قَبْلِهِمُ","translation":"তাদের আগে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6954,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْمَثُلَـٰتُ ۗ","translation":"শিক্ষামূলক দৃষ্টান্তসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6956,"position":10,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6957,"position":11,"arabic":"رَبَّكَ","translation":"তোমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6958,"position":12,"arabic":"لَذُو","translation":"অবশ্যই","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6959,"position":13,"arabic":"مَغْفِرَةٍۢ","translation":"সম্পন্ন ক্ষমাশীল","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6960,"position":14,"arabic":"لِّلنَّاسِ","translation":"মানুষের  জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6961,"position":15,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"সত্ত্বেও","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6962,"position":16,"arabic":"ظُلْمِهِمْ ۖ","translation":"তাদের সীমালঙ্ঘন","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6964,"position":17,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ","translation":"এবং নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6965,"position":18,"arabic":"رَبَّكَ","translation":"তোমার রব","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6966,"position":19,"arabic":"لَشَدِيدُ","translation":"অবশ্যই কঠোর","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6967,"position":20,"arabic":"ٱلْعِقَابِ","translation":"শাস্তিদানে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_006_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":6968,"position":21,"arabic":"٦","translation":"(৬)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":7,"arabic":"وَيَقُولُ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ لَوْلَآ أُنزِلَ عَلَيْهِ ءَايَةٌۭ مِّن رَّبِّهِۦٓ ۗ إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُنذِرٌۭ ۖ وَلِكُلِّ قَوْمٍ هَادٍ","translation":"However, they who are bent on denying the truth [refuse to believe and] say, \"Why has no miraculous sign ever been bestowed on him from on high by his Sustainer?\" [But] thou art only a warmer; and [in God] all people have a guide.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1714.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":8260,"position":1,"arabic":"وَيَقُولُ","translation":"এবং বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8261,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8262,"position":3,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","translation":"অস্বীকার করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8263,"position":4,"arabic":"لَوْلَآ","translation":"\"কেন না","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8264,"position":5,"arabic":"أُنزِلَ","translation":"অবতীর্ণ করা হলো","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8265,"position":6,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","translation":"তার উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8266,"position":7,"arabic":"ءَايَةٌۭ","translation":"কোনো নিদর্শন","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8267,"position":8,"arabic":"مِّن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8268,"position":9,"arabic":"رَّبِّهِۦٓ ۗ","translation":"তার রবের\"","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8270,"position":10,"arabic":"إِنَّمَآ","translation":"কেবল","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8271,"position":11,"arabic":"أَنتَ","translation":"তুমি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8272,"position":12,"arabic":"مُنذِرٌۭ ۖ","translation":"একজন সতর্ককারী","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8274,"position":13,"arabic":"وَلِكُلِّ","translation":"ও জন্যে প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8275,"position":14,"arabic":"قَوْمٍ","translation":"জাতির","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8276,"position":15,"arabic":"هَادٍ","translation":"একজন পথ প্রদর্শক (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_007_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":8277,"position":16,"arabic":"٧","translation":"(৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ يَعْلَمُ مَا تَحْمِلُ كُلُّ أُنثَىٰ وَمَا تَغِيضُ ٱلْأَرْحَامُ وَمَا تَزْدَادُ ۖ وَكُلُّ شَىْءٍ عِندَهُۥ بِمِقْدَارٍ","translation":"God knows what any female bears [in her womb], and by how much the wombs may fall short [in gestation], and by how much they may increase [the average period]: for with Him everything is [created] in accordance with its scope and purpose.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1715.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":9443,"position":1,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ তা'লা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9444,"position":2,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُ","translation":"জানেন","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9445,"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9446,"position":4,"arabic":"تَحْمِلُ","translation":"গর্ভধারণ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9447,"position":5,"arabic":"كُلُّ","translation":"প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9448,"position":6,"arabic":"أُنثَىٰ","translation":"নারী","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9449,"position":7,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং যা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9450,"position":8,"arabic":"تَغِيضُ","translation":"কমায়","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9451,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْحَامُ","translation":"জরায়ু","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9452,"position":10,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"ও যা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9453,"position":11,"arabic":"تَزْدَادُ ۖ","translation":"বাড়ায়","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9455,"position":12,"arabic":"وَكُلُّ","translation":"এবং প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9456,"position":13,"arabic":"شَىْءٍ","translation":"বস্তুর","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9457,"position":14,"arabic":"عِندَهُۥ","translation":"তাঁর কাছে (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9458,"position":15,"arabic":"بِمِقْدَارٍ","translation":"পরিমাণ নির্দিষ্ট","audioUrl":"wbw/013_008_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":9459,"position":16,"arabic":"٨","translation":"(৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":9,"arabic":"عَٰلِمُ ٱلْغَيْبِ وَٱلشَّهَٰدَةِ ٱلْكَبِيرُ ٱلْمُتَعَالِ","translation":"He knows all that is beyond the reach of a created being's perception as well as all that can be witnessed by a creature's senses or mind -the Great One, the One far above anything that is or could ever be!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1716.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":10594,"position":1,"arabic":"عَـٰلِمُ","translation":"তিনি জ্ঞানী","audioUrl":"wbw/013_009_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10595,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْغَيْبِ","translation":"অদৃশ্যের (সম্পর্কে)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_009_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10596,"position":3,"arabic":"وَٱلشَّهَـٰدَةِ","translation":"ও দৃশ্যের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_009_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10597,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْكَبِيرُ","translation":"তিনি মহান","audioUrl":"wbw/013_009_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10598,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْمُتَعَالِ","translation":"সর্বোচ্চ (মর্যাদাবান)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_009_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":10599,"position":6,"arabic":"٩","translation":"(৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":10,"arabic":"سَوَآءٌۭ مِّنكُم مَّنْ أَسَرَّ ٱلْقَوْلَ وَمَن جَهَرَ بِهِۦ وَمَنْ هُوَ مُسْتَخْفٍۭ بِٱلَّيْلِ وَسَارِبٌۢ بِٱلنَّهَارِ","translation":"It is all alike [to Him] whether any of you conceals his thought or brings it into the open, and whether he seeks to hide [his evil deeds] under the cover of night or walks [boldly] in the light of day,","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1717.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":11865,"position":1,"arabic":"سَوَآءٌۭ","translation":"(তারা) সমান","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11866,"position":2,"arabic":"مِّنكُم","translation":"তোমাদের মধ্য হ'তে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11867,"position":3,"arabic":"مَّنْ","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11868,"position":4,"arabic":"أَسَرَّ","translation":"গোপন করে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11869,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْقَوْلَ","translation":"কথা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11870,"position":6,"arabic":"وَمَن","translation":"ও যে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11871,"position":7,"arabic":"جَهَرَ","translation":"প্রকাশ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11872,"position":8,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"সম্পর্কে তা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11873,"position":9,"arabic":"وَمَنْ","translation":"এবং যে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11874,"position":10,"arabic":"هُوَ","translation":"সে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11875,"position":11,"arabic":"مُسْتَخْفٍۭ","translation":"আত্নগোপনকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11876,"position":12,"arabic":"بِٱلَّيْلِ","translation":"বেলায় রাতের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11877,"position":13,"arabic":"وَسَارِبٌۢ","translation":"ও বিচরণকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11878,"position":14,"arabic":"بِٱلنَّهَارِ","translation":"বেলায় দিনের","audioUrl":"wbw/013_010_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":11879,"position":15,"arabic":"١٠","translation":"(১০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":11,"arabic":"لَهُۥ مُعَقِّبَٰتٌۭ مِّنۢ بَيْنِ يَدَيْهِ وَمِنْ خَلْفِهِۦ يَحْفَظُونَهُۥ مِنْ أَمْرِ ٱللَّهِ ۗ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ لَا يُغَيِّرُ مَا بِقَوْمٍ حَتَّىٰ يُغَيِّرُوا۟ مَا بِأَنفُسِهِمْ ۗ وَإِذَآ أَرَادَ ٱللَّهُ بِقَوْمٍۢ سُوٓءًۭا فَلَا مَرَدَّ لَهُۥ ۚ وَمَا لَهُم مِّن دُونِهِۦ مِن وَالٍ","translation":"[thinking that] he has hosts of helpers-both such as can be perceived by him and such as are hidden from him -that could preserve him from whatever God may have willed. Verily, God does not change men's condition unless they change their inner selves; and when God wills people to suffer evil [in consequence of their own evil deeds], there is none who could avert it: for they have none who could protect them from Him.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1718.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":13147,"position":1,"arabic":"لَهُۥ","translation":"তার জন্যে (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/013_011_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13148,"position":2,"arabic":"مُعَقِّبَـٰتٌۭ","translation":"একের পর এক আগমনকারী প্রহরী","audioUrl":"wbw/013_011_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13149,"position":3,"arabic":"مِّنۢ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_011_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13150,"position":4,"arabic":"بَيْنِ","translation":"সামনে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_011_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13151,"position":5,"arabic":"يَدَيْهِ","translation":"তার","audioUrl":"wbw/013_011_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13152,"position":6,"arabic":"وَمِنْ","translation":"এবং থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_011_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13153,"position":7,"arabic":"خَلْفِهِۦ","translation":"তার পিছন","audioUrl":"wbw/013_011_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13154,"position":8,"arabic":"يَحْفَظُونَهُۥ","translation":"তাকে তারা রক্ষণাবেক্ষণ  করে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_011_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13155,"position":9,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"মধ্যে সে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_011_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":13156,"position":10,"arabic":"أَمْر